fix: v1.2.0 - iOS Standalone PWA auth fix

- Fix loading hang on iOS Add to Home Screen (Standalone mode)
- Use signInWithRedirect instead of signInWithPopup on iOS Standalone
- Await authReady (setPersistence) before subscribing onAuthStateChanged
- Handle getRedirectResult on app init for redirect flow
- Add PWA manifest.json with icons and display standalone
- Add apple-mobile-web-app-capable and theme-color meta tags via Next.js metadata
